trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow" /> objects in a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table" /> control.
A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> collection is returned by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control.
trans-unit.target: Ein <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> Auflistung wird zurückgegeben, durch die <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> Eigenschaft von der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> Steuerelement.

trans-unit.source: Only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> objects can be added to this <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Nur <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> können Objekte hinzugefügt werden, um dies <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection" />.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection" /> collection.
Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.Add%2A> method to add a new control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Verwenden der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.Add%2A> Methode, um ein neues Steuerelement zum Hinzufügen der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> Auflistung.

trans-unit.source: The specified control is added at the end of the array.
trans-unit.target: Das angegebene Steuerelement wird am Ende des Arrays hinzugefügt.

trans-unit.source: The control can be only an instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> control.
trans-unit.target: Das Steuerelement kann nur eine Instanz von einem <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> Steuerelement.

trans-unit.source: To add a control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> collection at a specific index location, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hinzufügen des Steuerelements an die <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> Auflistung an einer bestimmten Indexposition verwenden die <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> Methode.

trans-unit.source: The object specified by <paramref name="child" /> is not a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow" />.
The location in the array at which to add the child control.
The <see langword="Control" /> object to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection" />.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection" /> collection.
The new control is added to the array at the specified index location.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method to add a new control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> collection at a specified location.
trans-unit.target: Verwenden der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.AddAt%2A> Methode, um ein neues Steuerelement zum Hinzufügen der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> Auflistung am angegebenen Speicherort.

trans-unit.source: The control can be only an instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> control.
trans-unit.target: Das Steuerelement kann nur eine Instanz von einem <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> Steuerelement.

trans-unit.source: To add a control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> at the end of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection>, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hinzufügen des Steuerelements auf der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection> am Ende der <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection>, verwenden Sie die <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table.RowControlCollection.Add%2A> Methode.

trans-unit.source: The control does not allow child controls.
The child value is <see langword="null" />.
-or-
The object is not a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow" />.
